
HASHNODE
-google hashnode.com
-click on start your own blog
-sign in with your Email
-they will send you a link in ur email
-it will take you to a page
-click on "click here to sign in"
-fill your details:name,username,tagline (e.gprogrammer,youtuber,etc)
-click next
-enter your blog name e.g bukola kehinde's blog
-click next
-use hashnode subdomain(buquio.hashnode.dev)& select e.g buquiotest123
-click next
-click finish
-it will take you to your account
-click your pfofile pic
-it will show you menu bar
-click on "write new story"
-fill in youe title, content, images,sreenshots, links etc
-click publish
-check your blog name(on left corner):it will take u to ur home blog page
-then you can copy the url





MEDIUM
-google medium.com
-sign in with email
-it will send you a link
-click on the link in your email
-it will bring a form for you to fill
-type in ur name & username
-click create account
-select topics you are interested in e.g socialmedia etc
-click" continue to last step "(to right)
-click finish
-click write a story(top right)
-type title e.g "writing my first article"
-click "tell your story" to write your content(edit box,at bottom)
-click enter & click + => ðŸ“¸ > <> --
-click publish v arrow
-add tag e.g #writing #blogging etc
-click publish
-u can share to twitter etc
-u can copy url & share